# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Transparent Piano)

## Summary
The piano interface is now translucent and better integrated into the video feed.

## Visual Changes
- **Transparency**: The piano overlay is 60% opaque, allowing your hands to be seen "through" the keys.
- **Position**: Anchored firmly to the bottom 150px of the video feed.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal.
